node.text:
I promise to always stand by your side and honour you 
I am so excited to be your wife not only today but for the rest of our lives and share the journey of life with you and Rio as a family.
525,600 minutes a year 525,600 moments to be the best versions of ourselves for one another
I vow to support you to inspire you to show you how to be a superior man for me and therefore for the world. 
Because when you shine the world shines. 
When you’re overflowing you have so much to pour out onto the world. 
So I vow to always praise you, always touch you and you adore, always raise you up, always give you a Grammy when introducing you on club house 😉 
To always be addicted to one another, to listen to you to respect you. 
To be the best mother to our children. 
To be a phenomenal wife to you forever more. 

Michael, thank you for your love. I thank God every day for bringing me to you ♥️🙏🏼

My beautifully designed dress is by the number 1 Lebanese designer @danytabet

node.text:
Congratulations to the @fairmonttaghazoutbayresort for such an incredible opening of your hotel in Morroco ⭐️🙌🏽We were so honoured to be invited & had the most phenomenal time. Here’s A little sneak behind the scenes of what we got up to in this incredible resort last week! 
I can see why it was flooded with stars from around the world! The stuff were hands-down the best in the world and believe me I’ve travelled all over! Soooo grateful and we are excited to return again soon ❤️
Ps- Rio said he loveddd the kids club and the bucket & spade 🏝 🤪

node.text:
What are your New Years resolutions?

You don’t need to wait until December 31st at midnight to write your New Year’s resolutions. Every day is a new day every day is a new start every day is the beginning of your new year. Who says you can’t write them every single day. No one else controls your mind but YOU! no one else controls your outcome but you. YOU can literally write them any day anytime! 

Make your 10 year goal your 3 year goal then make your 3 year goal your 1 year goal! ☄️

node.text:
The road to success was always a lonely one for me and I know for so many others.. Every single day you have a choice to make- Who you’re gonna be that day. Who you’re going to show up as. Are you showing up in your highest self for yourself? ❣️
Are you friends with yourself? Because I know you wouldn’t speak those negative words to your friend and dishearten them. So why would you do it to yourself if your truly friends with yourself? 🙏🏼
 Are you showing up in your queen or king energy?
Because the only person you are letting down if you do not show up in this energy is YOURSELF ❣️
I keep my circle so tight, my true friends I can only count on 1 hand. Sure, I know a lot of people as I’m sure you do too but very few people I actually let  into my ‘inner circle’ and energy field. that’s because the more successful you become the more you have to be conscious about who you surround yourself with as it affects your direction. 
I had to learn to let go of so many people over the years as I’m sure you did, because toxic energies will only interfere with your long-term goals if you do not let them go. Learn to let go of what does not serve you and stand in your power!! Know it may feel lonely right now but soon it will all be worth it and the people around you at the top are the ones who serve you and empower you every day the same way you empower them. 
✨✨✨✨✨✨
